{"tid":478642,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"學生組織校外派港獨傳單 親中團體踩場對罵釀滋擾","createTime":"2017-11-24T09:39:53.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-24T10:27:39.000Z","uid":39464,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"3c480046a5068842007cfb2ac447773722de5ce5","tid":478642,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T09:39:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171124/large/1511513629_b4f6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171124%2Flarge%2F1511513629_b4f6.jpg&h=1db47f16&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n學生組織「學生動源」今日於葵涌循道中學外派發港獨傳單。不過，有傳校方今日特意安排有學生從後門放學，及後組織改到學校後門擺放旗幟，並插起寫着「香港獨立」的旗。<br />\n<br />\n該校中五生劉康上周出席校園記者活動時，手持港獨標語，「成功爭取」與特首林鄭月娥大合照<br />\n，遭校方警告。校方今午以安全理由，禁止劉康放學。學生動源發言人指，他們的活動會直至劉康出來為止。<br />\n<br />\n同時，親中團體「珍惜群組」到場反港獨，不斷大嗌「反港獨，港獨非常毒」口號，反問「香港獨立有咩好處」；又稱保護學子，速立23條，而雙方不時對罵。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20171124/57499670\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171124%2F57499670&d=Gh71wH31UTxdj3cGD%2F2x949%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=6c974420\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171124%2F57499670&h=61a9b698\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20171124/57499670</a>"},{"pid":"34eb4182b1e1a824534a8aa1625068e94e0778e4","tid":478642,"uid":141461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T10:24:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27a1e8ec0f6a2071b96d0474f40edae7bd0c8e82","tid":478642,"uid":141461,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T10:25:16.000Z","msg":"浩天哥吹緊暖氣SOR"},{"pid":"dc4aa000f25b99cac065f41724eaccb5b2e4bb95","tid":478642,"uid":2748,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy"